    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A mask that specifies the categories of local hardware events to enable during the event suppression interval. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/cgeventfiltermask",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can configure the system to suppress local hardware events from the keyboard or mouse during a short interval after a Quartz event is posted or during a synthetic mouse drag (mouse movement with the left or only mouse button down). For information about setting this local events filter, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/1408770-cgeventsourcesetlocaleventsfilte",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This function lets you specify an event source and a suppression state (event suppression interval or mouse drag), and returns a filter mask of event categories to be passed through during suppression.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
